{
  "stem": "9701.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I said to this student whose idea it was, but now, he's present even more than he's been before.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now what are we going to do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this future psychologist, I think, said, why don't you pick up the wet sponge, stand back from the board-- the blackboard, and throw it at this picture?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And see if you can erase him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I was doing it, there were just all kinds of feelings that came out of me that I wasn't even aware of.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I wasn't totally capable of erasing him by this one toss of the sponge.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I handed the sponge to the student whose idea it was, and he threw it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then the others threw it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the end, there was still a little bit left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, now what are we going to do?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the same student suggested that I pick up the chalk and just scratch him out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I just went, ah, ah, ah, and got rid of some more feelings.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And lo and behold, I now can do a little more than I could before.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like for instance, I can now work percentages, which I was tot-- totally unable to do before.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Interesting.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But back to the 30's, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] the next major thing, I guess, that happened was in 1936.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My grandfather, my mother's father, Heinrich Eichel H-E-I-N-R-I-C-H E-I-C-H-E-L, lived in Hanau, H-A-N-A-U.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one day, he was walking on the sidewalk when a Nazi came up to him and said, Jews aren't allowed to walk on the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Get off.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so he walked in the street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the same Nazi said, and Jews aren't allowed to walk on the side-- on the street, either.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
